Iron Heart
Level: Warblade 3
Prerequisite: One Iron Heart maneuver
Initiation Action: 1 standard action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: See text

Your fighting spirit, dedication, and training allow you to overcome almost anything to defeat your enemies. When you use this maneuver you end the strongest, spell, effect, or other condition currently affecting you and with a duration of 1 or more rounds. That effect ends immediately. You also surge with confidence and vengeance against your enemies, gaining a + 2 bonus on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.
